{
  "info": {
    "name": "Healthcare AI Triage - Clase 2 (n8n Local)",
    "description": "Pruebas del workflow extendido de clase 2.\n\nCambios vs clase 1:\n- Nuevo endpoint /webhook/patient-analysis-pdf (LlamaCloud)\n- Few-shot + top_p en el LLM\n- Validación de output schema\n- Logging estructurado + alertas\n\nPuerto: 5679 (el 5678 queda libre para clase-1).\n\nDos carpetas:\n- **JSON**: casos directos por body JSON (/webhook y /webhook-test)\n- **PDF**: ingesta por LlamaCloud (requiere LLAMA_CLOUD_API_KEY)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "healthcare-triage-clase-2"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:5679",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "webhookPath",
      "value": "/webhook/patient-analysis",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "webhookPathTest",
      "value": "/webhook-test/patient-analysis",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "webhookPathPdf",
      "value": "/webhook/patient-analysis-pdf",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "webhookPathPdfTest",
      "value": "/webhook-test/patient-analysis-pdf",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "samplePdfUrl",
      "value": "https://www.w3.org/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "PDF público de prueba (dummy). Reemplazar por un informe clínico real para ver el parsing completo."
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "JSON — producción (/webhook)",
      "description": "Workflow debe estar Active. Ver resultados en tab Executions.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "P1 — Crítico (vitales críticos + dolor torácico)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('priority P1_CRITICAL', () => pm.expect(b.triage.priority).to.eql('P1_CRITICAL'));",
                  "pm.test('SLA 5 min', () => pm.expect(b.triage.slaMinutes).to.eql(5));",
                  "pm.test('schemaValid true', () => pm.expect(b.schemaValid).to.be.true);",
                  "pm.test('fallbackUsed false', () => pm.expect(b.fallbackUsed).to.be.false);",
                  "pm.test('log con latencyMs', () => pm.expect(b.log.latencyMs).to.be.a('number'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}{{webhookPath}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}{{webhookPath}}"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"patientId\": \"P-C2-001\",\n  \"age\": 67,\n  \"symptoms\": \"dolor toracico intenso opresivo con disnea e irradiacion a brazo izquierdo\",\n  \"vitals\": { \"bp\": \"180/110\", \"hr\": 115, \"spo2\": 91 }\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "P2 — Alta (cefalea de alarma)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('priority ≤ P2', () => pm.expect(['P1_CRITICAL','P2_HIGH']).to.include(b.triage.priority));",
                  "pm.test('schemaValid true', () => pm.expect(b.schemaValid).to.be.true);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}{{webhookPath}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}{{webhookPath}}"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"patientId\": \"P-C2-002\",\n  \"age\": 54,\n  \"symptoms\": \"cefalea subita intensa thunderclap con vision borrosa y focalidad neurologica\",\n  \"vitals\": { \"bp\": \"160/95\", \"hr\": 88, \"spo2\": 97 }\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "P4 — Baja (consulta leve)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('priority P4_LOW', () => pm.expect(b.triage.priority).to.eql('P4_LOW'));",
                  "pm.test('SLA 24 hs', () => pm.expect(b.triage.slaMinutes).to.eql(1440));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}{{webhookPath}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}{{webhookPath}}"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"patientId\": \"P-C2-004\",\n  \"age\": 32,\n  \"symptoms\": \"dolor de garganta leve, congestion nasal, sin fiebre\",\n  \"vitals\": { \"hr\": 72, \"spo2\": 98 }\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Override — vitales críticos (dispara alerta)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('overrideApplied true', () => pm.expect(b.triage.overrideApplied).to.be.true);",
                  "pm.test('priority ≥ P2', () => pm.expect(['P1_CRITICAL','P2_HIGH']).to.include(b.triage.priority));",
                  "pm.test('log registra override', () => pm.expect(b.log.overrideApplied).to.be.true);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}{{webhookPath}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}{{webhookPath}}"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"patientId\": \"P-C2-005\",\n  \"age\": 28,\n  \"symptoms\": \"me siento un poco cansado\",\n  \"vitals\": { \"bp\": \"185/100\", \"hr\": 118, \"spo2\": 90 }\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Error 400 — falta symptoms",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 400', () => pm.response.to.have.status(400));",
                  "const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('mensaje cita symptoms', () => pm.expect(b.error).to.include('symptoms'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}{{webhookPath}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}{{webhookPath}}"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"patientId\": \"P-C2-006\",\n  \"age\": 50\n}"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
